DeBoer, Sid



NADA Board of Directors

Sidney B. DeBoer
Sidney B. DeBoer


                        Oregon
                    

Sidney B. "Sid" DeBoer is dealer principle of Lithia Chrysler, Dodge, Jeep in Ashland, Ore., and executive chairman of Lithia Motors Inc. He began an active career in the auto business in 1964, working in multiple positions at his father's dealership. In 1968 he founded Lithia Motors, which he has grown to its present size: 91 dealerships selling 27 brands in 11 states, and a public company trading on the New York Stock Exchange. DeBoer represents Oregon's franchised new-car dealers on the board of directors of the National Automobile Dealers Association. (Term: January 2014-January 2020)
Industry Service

Member, Oregon Auto Dealers Association, Medford New Car Dealers Association, Chrysler National Dealer Council, and American Import Automobile Dealers Association

Community Service

Board member, Southern Oregon University Foundation
Board member, Oregon Shakespeare Festival
Board member, Medford Chamber of Commerce
Founder and president, Sid and Karen DeBoer Foundation, which has issued grants to charities exceeding $2.8 million as part of the Oregon Community Foundation
DeBoer has been involved with and donates to many organizations including Southern Oregon University, the Ashland Community Hospital Foundation, Community Works, Elks Club International, Medford Rogue Rotary, Oregon Community Foundation, Oregon Shakespeare Festival, Providence Hospital Foundation, Rogue Valley Medical Center Foundation, St. Mary's High School, United Way of Jackson County, and the University of Oregon

Awards

Time Magazine Quality Dealer Award for Oregon
Sports Illustrated All-Star Dealer Award
President's Medal, Southern Oregon University
Various Medford and Ashland Chamber of Commerce Awards
Dealership awards include Honda Dealer Awards, Chrysler Corporation 5-Star Dealer Awards, Toyota's President's Awards, and the coveted Porsche Premier Dealer Award

Education

Stanford University
University of Oregon





                     Lithia Chrysler, Dodge, Jeep
 234 Vista Street
 Ashland, OR 97520www.lithia.com


 Franchises

Chrysler, Dodge, Jeep, Ram




